Achievements.Name: Completionist
Achievements.Description: Accomplish all of the achievements in the game.

Achievements.Name: A New Hero
Achievements.Description: View any of the endings using a custom character.

Achievements.Name: A Special Gift
Achievements.Description: Receive a weapon or item as a gift for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Age of Beauty
Achievements.Description: Have at least three officers declare their love for you in a single lifetime.

Achievements.Name: Aim For The Back
Achievements.Description: Perform a betrayal for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Appointed Marshal
Achievements.Description: Be appointed as a Marshal for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Appointed Strategist
Achievements.Description: Be appointed as a Strategist for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Architect
Achievements.Description: Build a facility for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Battle Ready
Achievements.Description: Obtain at least 30 items.

Achievements.Name: Battlefield Controller
Achievements.Description: Capture 10 or more bases during a single battle.

Achievements.Name: Beginnings of Ambition
Achievements.Description: Raise the banner of your own Kingdom for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Beyond Invincible
Achievements.Description: Use any custom character to defeat all of the famous officers.

Achievements.Name: Blossoming Love
Achievements.Description: Profess your love for someone or have someone confess their love for you for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Brave and Bold
Achievements.Description: Fight your way into enemy territory alone and defeat an officer.

Achievements.Name: Building Trust
Achievements.Description: Complete a Quest and deepen your friendship with your Ruler.

Achievements.Name: Construction Enthusiast
Achievements.Description: Build at least six of the same facility.

Achievements.Name: Crushing Victory
Achievements.Description: Win a battle with more than 90% of your total forces remaining.

Achievements.Name: Decorated Veteran
Achievements.Description: Achieve all titles.

Achievements.Name: Doesn't Play Well With Others
Achievements.Description: Have a subordinate officer abandon you for the first time.

Achievements.Name: First Mission
Achievements.Description: Complete your first mission.

Achievements.Name: Goal Orientated Leader
Achievements.Description: Complete four Battle Objectives in a single battle.

Achievements.Name: Husk of Evil
Achievements.Description: Obtain virtue of "Pure Evil."

Achievements.Name: Intellectual Victory
Achievements.Description: Defeat more than 10,000 enemies using just Stratagems.

Achievements.Name: Jumping Ahead
Achievements.Description: Get recruited as a Marshal or Strategist from being a Free Officer.

Achievements.Name: King of Chaos
Achievements.Description: Clear any scenario on the "Chaos" difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Many Ways To Live
Achievements.Description: Complete all lifestyles.

Achievements.Name: Master of Strategy
Achievements.Description: Execute all Strategy Commands at least once.

Achievements.Name: Nepotism Rules
Achievements.Description: Create a Kingdom comprised entirely of your sworn siblings, spouses and children.

Achievements.Name: Oath Beneath Peach Trees
Achievements.Description: Swear a sworn sibling oath for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Paragon of Good
Achievements.Description: Obtain virtue of "Saint."

Achievements.Name: Prove Your Quality
Achievements.Description: Became a Ruler for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Rebel
Achievements.Description: Rise in rebellion and become Ruler.

Achievements.Name: Sizable Kingdom
Achievements.Description: Obtain 20 officers in your own Kingdom.

Achievements.Name: Start of a Long Road
Achievements.Description: Complete a Strategy Objective for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Strategy Stopper
Achievements.Description: Stop a Large Scale Stratagem being prepared by the enemy.

Achievements.Name: Successor
Achievements.Description: Succeed your superior's position for the first time.

Achievements.Name: The Elite Few
Achievements.Description: Win a battle with significantly less allied forces than enemy ones.

Achievements.Name: The Sound of Tiny Feet
Achievements.Description: Have a total of at least 5 children.

Achievements.Name: Till Death Do Us Part
Achievements.Description: Get married for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Nation
Achievements.Description: Make all famous officers into your subordinate officers.

Achievements.Name: Unrivaled Strategist
Achievements.Description: Use at least 100 Stratagems.

Achievements.Name: Weapons Locker
Achievements.Description: Obtain at least 100 weapons.

Achievements.Name: Collected Works
Achievements.Description: In Edit Mode, create at least one officer, banner, warhorse and soldier.

Achievements.Name: Many Crossroads
Achievements.Description: View all of the events that can be watched in the Gallery.

Achievements.Name: The Next Generation
Achievements.Description: Have a child for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Weather Master
Achievements.Description: Use a Stratagem to change the weather.

Achievements.Name: Well Seasoned
Achievements.Description: Fight and win a stage in spring, summer, fall and winter.

Achievements.Name: Winds of Victory
Achievements.Description: Take part in "Battle of Chibi - Allied Forces" & have Zhuge Liang's "Southeast Wind" strategy work.
